accessibility.text: LED Tower becomes central figure, the brain of MGM. It is an intelligent life form, personage, ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE. It knows a lot and sees everything around, communicates with visitors via interactive visualizations and applications.
It is a portal to the infinite world of information / universe. Gateway to things that are not here and now (geography / cosmos / depths of Earth / microcosmos / human intelligence).
